                    <comment id="12572822" author="jukkaz" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2008 08:23:26 +0000"  >Applied the product patch (without the &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1116&quot; title=&quot;Database persistence managers: log database and driver name and version&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-1116&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changes) in revision 631371.&lt;br/&gt;
